Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.84,0:00:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,（奥田咲）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.15,0:00:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.08,0:00:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.69,0:00:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,学校怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.69,0:01:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,一般般啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.36,0:01:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,什么叫一般般
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.96,0:01:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么了你的脸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.36,0:01:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,只是摔了一跤
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.77,0:01:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,那很痛的样子\N有没有去医院
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.77,0:01:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,没有必要去医院吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.37,0:01:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,衣服呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.51,0:01:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,摔跤的时候弄脏了\N把它放包里了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.91,0:01:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,那就放洗衣机里面去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.58,0:01:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,不要紧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.91,0:01:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,还有别的地方弄伤了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.78,0:01:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,不要紧的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.45,0:01:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我回自己房间了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.46,0:01:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,最近他状态一直都不是很好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.66,0:01:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,之前从学校回来\N什么都跟我讲的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.00,0:01:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,这孩子也到了\N令人难以琢磨的年纪了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.95,0:02:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,有没有把衣服放洗衣机里面
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.58,0:02:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我去放
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.71,0:02:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,这实在是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.45,0:02:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,这上面怎么有血
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.52,0:02:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,难道说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.92,0:02:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,被欺负了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.94,0:03:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,好疼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.56,0:03:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,这什么情况
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.30,0:03:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.30,0:03:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么可能没什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.37,0:03:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你被欺负了吗 跟我讲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.84,0:03:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,只是摔跤而已\N我要学习你快出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.91,0:03:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么可能呢 别这样说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.85,0:03:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是家人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.98,0:03:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我们一起努力解快吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.79,0:03:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,好烦 我要学习快出去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.60,0:04:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,才没有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.67,0:04:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,没有欺负这种事情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.21,0:04:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,完全不是你想那样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.61,0:04:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.28,0:04:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,别打扰我了 快出去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.32,0:04:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,他以前不是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.26,0:05:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,但是不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.20,0:05:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我是站在你这一边的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.80,0:05:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,这件事我来帮你处理吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.08,0:05:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,（又漂亮又温柔）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.68,0:05:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,（令我自豪的母亲）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.42,0:05:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,（却被下流的）\N（不良前辈被侵犯了）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.96,0:05:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,（而我却看到了这一切）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.83,0:05:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,（别来上学了）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.90,0:05:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,（把钱拿来）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.91,0:05:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,（你这个傻瓜）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.39,0:06:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,正人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.16,0:06:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我瞒着儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.76,0:06:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,为了处理\N那些令人讨厌的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.10,0:06:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我开始行动了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.17,0:06:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我经常联系我那些朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.97,0:06:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,偶尔也会到我儿子的房间里面
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.11,0:07:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,终于找到了欺负我儿子的犯人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.85,0:07:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,（数日后）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.40,0:08:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,懂了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.08,0:08:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你想说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.28,0:08:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我想让你停止对我儿子的欺凌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.69,0:08:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,不是你想的这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.49,0:08:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,在我们玩的更开心的时候\N是他先打扰我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.97,0:09:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,也许原因在于我儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.50,0:09:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,这一点我会道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.44,0:09:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,但是互相欺凌也没什么意思\N不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.45,0:09:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么说我们在欺负他
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.78,0:09:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,就因为我长得这个样子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.86,0:09:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你是凭感觉判断我的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.86,0:09:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.26,0:09:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,没有那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.00,0:09:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,如果伤到你我表示抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.67,0:09:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你有诚意道歉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.47,0:09:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,如果真的有诚意道歉的话\N你把他带过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.41,0:09:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,现在带他过来是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.62,0:09:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,他在这个时候\N一般都在上补习班
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.16,0:09:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,连诚意都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.76,0:09:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,没这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.96,0:10:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,那你跪下来磕头给我道歉认错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.63,0:10:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,什么年代了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.43,0:10:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,为了解快你儿子的事情\N才过来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.77,0:10:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你没有诚意我也很难办
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.38,0:10:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,但是这种
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.72,0:10:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,算了算了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.32,0:10:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,他也真不容易啊\N有你这样的母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.87,0:10:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.08,0:10:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,原谅儿子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.61,0:11:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,自从我丈夫离开我之后\N他是我唯一的家人了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.49,0:11:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,为了儿子我什么都能做
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.49,0:11:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,他对我而言是不可替代的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.30,0:11:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你有诚意吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.90,0:11:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,一点诚意都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.98,0:11:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是道歉了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.65,0:11:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,下跪谁都能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.12,0:11:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,就是因为他的原因\N才会变成这个样子不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.19,0:11:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.19,0:11:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,母亲不应该替她承担责任吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.27,0:11:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是道歉了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.87,0:11:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你会说什么都会做吗\N那快点脱掉衣服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.01,0:11:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.68,0:12:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了\N你已经没有多少分的诚意了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.42,0:12:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以先回去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.09,0:12:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.03,0:12:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你别浪费时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.10,0:12:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,脱了就好了不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.24,0:12:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.44,0:12:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,快点脱掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.71,0:12:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,脱掉之后来好好道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.89,0:13:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.43,0:13:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,没有诚意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.10,0:13:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,能不能好好道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.31,0:13:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.51,0:13:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,抬头吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.19,0:13:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,放手 阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.93,0:13:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你的身材好淫荡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.93,0:14:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,居然没有丈夫也太浪费了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.61,0:14:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.35,0:14:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我会原谅他的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.15,0:14:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.82,0:14:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,当然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.96,0:14:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.30,0:14:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,比起这个 不如稍微
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.97,0:14:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,陪我玩一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.97,0:14:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你要干什么快停下来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.17,0:14:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,等等快停下来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.72,0:14:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你要干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.25,0:14:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,不要逃跑啊\N你 有什么不好的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.27,0:15:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,快停下来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.87,0:15:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,真的可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.14,0:15:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,让你儿子断绝社交往来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.68,0:15:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.28,0:15:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,但是你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.35,0:15:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,不觉得原因都在你这边吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.22,0:15:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,他的立场会更加严峻吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.49,0:15:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.56,0:15:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,好疼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.16,0:15:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.50,0:15:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,快放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.63,0:15:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,用你的身体来支付吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.44,0:15:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,这样子我也会保密的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.44,0:15:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,等等快停下来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.58,0:15:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,这胸部真的很不错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.91,0:15:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,快停下来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.12,0:15:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我不愿意呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.86,0:16:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,快放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.73,0:16:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你是真的吗认真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.67,0:16:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你应该很久没有过了\N很兴奋对不对呀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.80,0:16:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,别这样子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.54,0:16:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你看乳头都变硬了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.35,0:16:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,等一等
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.89,0:16:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,快停下来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.45,0:17:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,好柔软啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.62,0:17:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是已经道歉过了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.49,0:17:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,所以说\N我才想要借用你的身体呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.76,0:17:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,有什么不好的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.78,0:18:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.65,0:18:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,等一等
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.93,0:18:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样有感觉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.53,0:18:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,等一等
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.75,0:18:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,快停下来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.45,0:19:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,真的不可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.06,0:19:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,快停下来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.92,0:19:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,这怎么能行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.75,0:19:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,等一等
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.44,0:20:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,不行了快点下来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.51,0:20:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.12,0:20:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你要干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.06,0:20:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,阿姨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.99,0:20:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你是不是被强上很爽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.67,0:20:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.67,0:20:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,来摸一摸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.81,0:20:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,来摸一摸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.08,0:20:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,因为你我才变成这个样子的\N你要好好负责哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.49,0:21:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.49,0:21:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你应该知道怎么做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.97,0:21:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,快一点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.85,0:21:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,不要紧的我会好好陪你玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.25,0:21:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我会好好替你保密的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.86,0:21:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.99,0:21:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我会保证的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.80,0:21:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你不欺负他了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.87,0:21:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你不信任我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.34,0:21:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我会好好守约的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.40,0:22:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,这样很柔软对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.87,0:22:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,用手就够了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.90,0:23:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.59,0:23:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,对你丈夫比起来怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.26,0:23:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,不要问这个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.20,0:23:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.87,0:24:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,那你用胸部来帮我夹住吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.74,0:24:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,快点像这样子来取下来\N快点更舒服一点
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.22,0:24:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.09,0:24:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.51,0:24:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,果然还是很棒的这感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.79,0:25:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,阿姨这个地方是不是很敏感
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.67,0:25:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,自己摩擦是不是很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.35,0:25:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,来感受一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.18,0:25:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,快来吧舔一下
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.13,0:26:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你也不用这么盯着我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.91,0:27:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.34,0:27:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,真的好淫荡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.01,0:27:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,太棒了过来一下吧快点
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.69,0:27:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,到这边来
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.89,0:27:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,腿张开
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.03,0:27:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,这不挺好的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.71,0:28:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,都已经湿透了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.44,0:28:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,看都已经这副模样了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.80,0:28:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我也很喜欢舔的
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.32,0:29:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.94,0:29:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,忍不住吗等等不要这样子
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.88,0:29:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,要这样子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.88,0:29:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,这有什么不好的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.42,0:29:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,就让我试一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.42,0:29:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.22,0:29:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,那真的好吗都这副模样了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.23,0:30:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,戴套
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.37,0:30:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,哦有套就可以了对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.10,0:30:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,这样就可以原谅我了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.92,0:30:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,这样可以了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.86,0:30:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你阿姨把小穴张开
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.40,0:30:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我来把它搞进去
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.17,0:31:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.71,0:31:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,有点不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.14,0:31:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.82,0:32:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,有点不妙啊你的小穴
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.36,0:32:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.72,0:32:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,高潮了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.19,0:32:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你是高潮了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.53,0:32:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.80,0:32:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,真的没有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.73,0:32:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,很久没有尝试过了吧\N这种感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.34,0:33:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧尽情的弄起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.89,0:33:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,看着我的脸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.93,0:33:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,不行啊不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.80,0:34:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.43,0:34:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,要不要好好的干一干啊
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.75,0:35:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.69,0:35:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,真的是很敏感啊
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.57,0:35:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,还能自己动吗
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.18,0:35:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,准备好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.05,0:35:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.80,0:36:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧动起来
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.99,0:37:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,不行了不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.60,0:37:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,来更快一点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.76,0:37:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,来到另外一边来
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.27,0:38:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.75,0:38:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.13,0:39:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.67,0:39:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,还没那么快呢
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.79,0:40:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,就已经结束了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.06,0:40:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,已经够了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.19,0:40:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你可能已经爽了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.13,0:40:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,但我还没高潮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.76,0:41:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,这样会更舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.20,0:41:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,有点不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.43,0:42:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,真的是好棒啊你觉得呢
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.50,0:42:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,不行了不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.66,0:42:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,想要弄进去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.59,0:42:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,这样很快就结束了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.62,0:43:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,要射了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.42,0:43:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,要射了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.84,0:43:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,真是舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.98,0:43:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,要舔干净
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.07,0:44:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.21,0:44:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,今后为了不让你儿子被欺负
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.02,0:44:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你要随时做好做爱的准备哦
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.22,0:44:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.63,0:46:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,原来不仅仅是那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.17,0:47:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,他时不时来我家
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.51,0:47:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,以我儿子为威胁\N玩弄我的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.94,0:47:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,快停下来
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.48,0:47:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,这个时候你不上学吗
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.88,0:47:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我才不想上学呢
Dialogue: 0,0:47:39.28,0:47:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,而且这边的阿姨的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.15,0:47:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,可能让我更舒服一点哦
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.69,0:47:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.83,0:47:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你老实一点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.25,0:48:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你能说这种话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:48:13.32,0:48:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你不想让你儿子不受欺负吗
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.86,0:48:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你不要这样子
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.40,0:48:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我该怎么做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.00,0:48:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我总不能跟他\N你妈在跟我做爱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.68,0:48:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得呢
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.82,0:48:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得该怎么做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.29,0:48:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,这边都已经湿透了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.76,0:49:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,有点不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.04,0:49:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,而且我
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.64,0:49:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,很喜欢你柔软的胸部
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.71,0:49:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你丈夫有对你的胸\N做出评价吗
Dialogue: 0,0:49:50.21,0:49:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,已经足够了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.55,0:49:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,完全没有满足的
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.97,0:50:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样嘴巴不要停
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.73,0:50:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,再多过来一点
Dialogue: 0,0:51:01.62,0:51:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你多大了
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.42,0:51:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,这屁股很柔软哦
Dialogue: 0,0:51:13.36,0:51:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.24,0:51:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,像笨蛋一样这么有感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.91,0:51:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你应该很喜欢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.99,0:51:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,插进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:04.22,0:52:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,这一个地方吗
Dialogue: 0,0:52:06.48,0:52:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.29,0:52:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.11,0:52:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:52:41.32,0:52:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,对的阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.12,0:52:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你现在的样\N跟AV没什么两样
Dialogue: 0,0:52:51.60,0:52:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我满足你了你能停下来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.73,0:52:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,看情况吧
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.95,0:53:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我超喜欢这种的
Dialogue: 0,0:53:51.92,0:53:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.94,0:54:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,不要快停下来
Dialogue: 0,0:54:11.94,0:54:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:54:14.48,0:54:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,高潮了
Dialogue: 0,0:54:29.56,0:54:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,来坐下来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.93,0:55:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:55:05.60,0:55:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,有感觉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.81,0:55:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.56,0:55:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不行了不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:55:41.10,0:55:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,要高潮了
Dialogue: 0,0:55:45.90,0:55:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,要高潮了
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.37,0:55:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,要高潮了
Dialogue: 0,0:55:59.25,0:56:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,果然跟阿姨做爱真舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:56:28.61,0:56:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,不行了不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:56:45.03,0:56:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,不行快停下来
Dialogue: 0,0:56:55.17,0:56:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,不行要高潮了
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.78,0:57:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,要高潮了
Dialogue: 0,0:57:24.14,0:57:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:57:26.54,0:57:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,不要要高潮了
Dialogue: 0,0:57:57.50,0:57:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,真的是好棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:58:19.52,0:58:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,一直都这么爽吗
Dialogue: 0,0:58:22.73,0:58:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:58:25.00,0:58:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,这样很兴奋对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:58:28.33,0:58:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:58:45.55,0:58:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:58:51.82,0:58:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,不行了不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:59:09.97,0:59:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,真是开心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:59:21.19,0:59:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:59:27.86,0:59:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,那就不管他了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:59:34.00,0:59:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,不要欺负我儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:59:38.00,0:59:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,那就看你了
Dialogue: 0,0:59:47.48,0:59:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我们打个赌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:59:51.35,0:59:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,阿姨这个
Dialogue: 0,0:59:56.82,0:59:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,喜欢吧
Dialogue: 0,1:00:02.56,1:00:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,有没有对乳头搞高潮过
Dialogue: 0,1:00:12.04,1:00:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,那我来慢慢来吧
Dialogue: 0,1:00:16.04,1:00:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,如果舒服的话
Dialogue: 0,1:00:19.78,1:00:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,那我就不欺负他
Dialogue: 0,1:00:23.25,1:00:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,1:00:25.65,1:00:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我会守约的
Dialogue: 0,1:00:27.52,1:00:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,要一言为定哦
Dialogue: 0,1:00:31.66,1:00:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,那就可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,1:00:56.75,1:00:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了呀
Dialogue: 0,1:01:07.83,1:01:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,感谢老婆对不对啊
Dialogue: 0,1:01:14.50,1:01:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,还是很喜欢对吧
Dialogue: 0,1:01:29.45,1:01:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,这样是不是很喜欢啊
Dialogue: 0,1:01:39.72,1:01:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,1:01:46.80,1:01:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,1:01:57.21,1:01:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,靠近一点嘛
Dialogue: 0,1:01:58.94,1:02:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以不可以
Dialogue: 0,1:02:09.62,1:02:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,不行了不行了
Dialogue: 0,1:02:36.45,1:02:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,阿姨你一直在忍耐吗
Dialogue: 0,1:02:41.65,1:02:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,都这么湿润了
Dialogue: 0,1:02:48.46,1:02:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,都被都被你搞脏了
Dialogue: 0,1:03:06.88,1:03:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,这是为了我儿子
Dialogue: 0,1:03:42.25,1:03:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,学习还顺利吗
Dialogue: 0,1:03:43.98,1:03:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,还顺利
Dialogue: 0,1:03:46.52,1:03:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,大嫂过来你要喝吗
Dialogue: 0,1:03:49.99,1:03:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,1:04:03.47,1:04:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,学校还顺利吗
Dialogue: 0,1:04:05.47,1:04:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,顺利啊
Dialogue: 0,1:04:08.81,1:04:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,快考试了 大伙都在学习
Dialogue: 0,1:04:13.61,1:04:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,而且经常有考试
Dialogue: 0,1:04:19.08,1:04:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你跟你朋友怎么样
Dialogue: 0,1:04:22.69,1:04:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,很普通啊偶尔做一做笔记
Dialogue: 0,1:04:27.36,1:04:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯今天周日要去朋友家
Dialogue: 0,1:04:29.89,1:04:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,可能不太需要吃午饭
Dialogue: 0,1:04:31.63,1:04:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,那太好了
Dialogue: 0,1:04:34.03,1:04:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了你好好努力吧
Dialogue: 0,1:04:36.57,1:04:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我会努力的
Dialogue: 0,1:05:04.86,1:05:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,1:05:07.40,1:05:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,没有被欺负了
Dialogue: 0,1:05:12.07,1:05:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,看样子他守约了
Dialogue: 0,1:05:52.51,1:05:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,不要突然来我家好吗
Dialogue: 0,1:05:55.05,1:05:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经有点蠢蠢欲动了
Dialogue: 0,1:05:58.52,1:06:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你来陪陪我吧
Dialogue: 0,1:06:13.46,1:06:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,不要这样
Dialogue: 0,1:06:18.80,1:06:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,快点来吧
Dialogue: 0,1:06:29.75,1:06:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你搞什么
Dialogue: 0,1:06:32.15,1:06:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我以为你有点蠢蠢欲动了
Dialogue: 0,1:06:35.89,1:06:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,快停下
Dialogue: 0,1:06:49.10,1:06:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,事到如今无所谓了吧
Dialogue: 0,1:06:52.84,1:06:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,等等不要这样子
Dialogue: 0,1:07:14.99,1:07:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,快来吧
Dialogue: 0,1:07:40.75,1:07:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,帮我舔一下
Dialogue: 0,1:07:43.69,1:07:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,1:08:03.44,1:08:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,自己动起来
Dialogue: 0,1:08:26.40,1:08:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,快来
Dialogue: 0,1:08:36.01,1:08:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,1:08:50.69,1:08:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,1:08:52.29,1:08:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,好好舔一舔
Dialogue: 0,1:09:15.38,1:09:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你这边都湿透了
Dialogue: 0,1:09:21.52,1:09:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,应该兴奋了吧
Dialogue: 0,1:09:23.79,1:09:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有
Dialogue: 0,1:09:30.33,1:09:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧快点
Dialogue: 0,1:09:57.02,1:09:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,再让我舒服一下吧
Dialogue: 0,1:11:00.82,1:11:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,好好动起来吧
Dialogue: 0,1:11:32.05,1:11:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,再激烈一点吗
Dialogue: 0,1:12:32.78,1:12:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,那好好舔一舔吧
Dialogue: 0,1:13:32.04,1:13:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,谁让你吐出来的
Dialogue: 0,1:13:34.70,1:13:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,快停下来
Dialogue: 0,1:13:49.92,1:13:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,要射了
Dialogue: 0,1:13:52.86,1:13:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,要射了
Dialogue: 0,1:14:05.14,1:14:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,快弄干争吧
Dialogue: 0,1:14:26.89,1:14:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我们继续做到最后吧
Dialogue: 0,1:14:32.90,1:14:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,可以的吧
Dialogue: 0,1:14:35.43,1:14:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,反正你也想做对不对啊
Dialogue: 0,1:14:39.30,1:14:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,那让他变大吧
Dialogue: 0,1:14:51.71,1:14:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,内裤都湿透了
Dialogue: 0,1:14:58.12,1:14:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样啊
Dialogue: 0,1:15:00.26,1:15:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,插进去了
Dialogue: 0,1:15:02.66,1:15:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,1:15:04.93,1:15:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,来嘛
Dialogue: 0,1:15:07.06,1:15:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系的吧
Dialogue: 0,1:15:18.94,1:15:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,1:15:20.81,1:15:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,快停一下
Dialogue: 0,1:15:22.95,1:15:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,都到如今
Dialogue: 0,1:15:38.70,1:15:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,1:15:40.70,1:15:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你干嘛不接电话啊
Dialogue: 0,1:15:46.44,1:15:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟别人在做事
Dialogue: 0,1:15:52.44,1:15:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,不是你都没怎么理人啊
Dialogue: 0,1:15:56.58,1:15:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你有女朋友了吗
Dialogue: 0,1:15:59.78,1:16:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,差不多吧
Dialogue: 0,1:16:03.25,1:16:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么啦 你跟女人玩了吗
Dialogue: 0,1:16:06.99,1:16:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,但是也没有这么简单就可以搞
Dialogue: 0,1:16:13.40,1:16:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,居然把我抛在一边玩\N开心的事情
Dialogue: 0,1:16:17.93,1:16:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,1:16:19.54,1:16:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,到时候叫我
Dialogue: 0,1:16:21.54,1:16:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我刚才都说了
Dialogue: 0,1:16:23.94,1:16:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,他不是你喜欢那种年轻的人
Dialogue: 0,1:16:28.88,1:16:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,那是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,1:16:33.55,1:16:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,就是跟班里同学的母亲在玩
Dialogue: 0,1:16:39.69,1:16:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你什么样子
Dialogue: 0,1:16:43.83,1:16:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,叫我们过来
Dialogue: 0,1:16:47.56,1:16:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,1:16:49.17,1:16:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了吗
Dialogue: 0,1:16:51.83,1:16:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,1:16:55.04,1:16:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,那就拜托啦
Dialogue: 0,1:17:08.38,1:17:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,阿姨我下次再来
Dialogue: 0,1:18:18.59,1:18:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,因为不是很愿意但为什么
Dialogue: 0,1:18:41.81,1:18:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈谢谢
Dialogue: 0,1:18:43.81,1:18:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈的饭很好吃
Dialogue: 0,1:18:45.68,1:18:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,1:18:52.76,1:18:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,今天好努力哦
Dialogue: 0,1:18:55.29,1:18:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我会努力的
Dialogue: 0,1:19:01.83,1:19:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,真好吃
Dialogue: 0,1:19:13.98,1:19:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,看你好像很努力学习\N但是我做点好吃的给你吃
Dialogue: 0,1:19:21.05,1:19:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,1:19:22.65,1:19:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,想吃什么
Dialogue: 0,1:19:23.99,1:19:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,该怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,1:19:25.86,1:19:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,牛肉火锅
Dialogue: 0,1:19:26.79,1:19:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,牛肉火锅是吗
Dialogue: 0,1:19:27.86,1:19:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,1:19:28.52,1:19:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈谢谢
Dialogue: 0,1:19:33.60,1:19:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,好开心啊
Dialogue: 0,1:19:35.33,1:19:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈的菜很好吃
Dialogue: 0,1:19:38.13,1:19:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,1:19:38.94,1:19:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我很期待
Dialogue: 0,1:19:41.34,1:19:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我要好好努力学习了
Dialogue: 0,1:19:43.07,1:19:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,努力吧
Dialogue: 0,1:19:47.08,1:19:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,最近有没有什么变化呢\N学校的生活
Dialogue: 0,1:19:50.01,1:19:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么变化啊很开心啊
Dialogue: 0,1:19:52.15,1:19:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,开心吗那就好
Dialogue: 0,1:19:57.89,1:20:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,即便如此只要能\N守护儿子的笑容我也觉得值了
Dialogue: 0,1:20:07.10,1:20:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样啊感觉
Dialogue: 0,1:20:10.57,1:20:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,这边都已经湿透了
Dialogue: 0,1:20:33.92,1:20:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,不行要高潮了
Dialogue: 0,1:20:40.33,1:20:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,又高潮了吗
Dialogue: 0,1:20:51.67,1:20:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,来再爽一下吧
Dialogue: 0,1:21:02.89,1:21:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,与此同时
Dialogue: 0,1:21:05.42,1:21:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟他做爱的程度\N也越来越激烈了
Dialogue: 0,1:21:10.89,1:21:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,一开始是一周两次
Dialogue: 0,1:21:13.16,1:21:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,后来一周三次
Dialogue: 0,1:21:14.63,1:21:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,现在一周4次
Dialogue: 0,1:21:16.77,1:21:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,前天在儿子房间里做爱了
Dialogue: 0,1:21:24.91,1:21:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,1:21:44.93,1:21:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧快点
Dialogue: 0,1:22:12.56,1:22:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,插进去了
Dialogue: 0,1:22:41.25,1:22:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,好动起来啊
Dialogue: 0,1:23:06.08,1:23:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,要高潮了
Dialogue: 0,1:23:41.44,1:23:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,保姆你应该很兴奋吧
Dialogue: 0,1:23:47.58,1:23:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,在儿子的房间\N里面很兴奋是吗
Dialogue: 0,1:23:49.45,1:23:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,不要这样
Dialogue: 0,1:23:53.59,1:23:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,今天就好好爽爽吧\N等一下前辈要过来了
Dialogue: 0,1:23:59.60,1:24:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你要比平时还要努力哦
Dialogue: 0,1:24:13.21,1:24:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,又变湿润了
Dialogue: 0,1:24:16.15,1:24:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧快点
Dialogue: 0,1:24:37.37,1:24:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,1:24:50.98,1:24:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,1:25:08.73,1:25:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,不行不行啊
Dialogue: 0,1:25:13.14,1:25:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,1:25:29.42,1:25:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,真的是很容易高潮
Dialogue: 0,1:25:49.84,1:25:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,1:25:51.57,1:25:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,很棒的声音哦
Dialogue: 0,1:25:59.58,1:26:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,不行了不行了
Dialogue: 0,1:26:06.92,1:26:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,1:26:16.40,1:26:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,这么猛的吗
Dialogue: 0,1:26:25.47,1:26:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,汗都已经湿透了
Dialogue: 0,1:26:30.81,1:26:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,不要紧吧你
Dialogue: 0,1:27:07.65,1:27:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,1:27:19.40,1:27:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,喂你在这里吧
Dialogue: 0,1:27:22.87,1:27:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你是先搞了吗
Dialogue: 0,1:27:32.88,1:27:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,不得了
Dialogue: 0,1:27:35.41,1:27:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我都叫你等我一下了
Dialogue: 0,1:27:38.75,1:27:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,1:27:39.15,1:27:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,1:27:45.15,1:27:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,就是这一位吗
Dialogue: 0,1:27:46.89,1:27:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,1:27:49.69,1:27:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,不错 初次见面
Dialogue: 0,1:27:53.03,1:27:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我是你儿子的新朋友
Dialogue: 0,1:28:00.37,1:28:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你别先偷跑啊
Dialogue: 0,1:28:03.57,1:28:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我想先热一下场而已
Dialogue: 0,1:28:05.04,1:28:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,那我可以先搞吗
Dialogue: 0,1:28:10.91,1:28:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,那阿姨你就好好陪前辈玩吧
Dialogue: 0,1:28:24.66,1:28:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好柔软啊
Dialogue: 0,1:28:28.13,1:28:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,好好玩一玩吧
Dialogue: 0,1:28:30.27,1:28:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,把手拿开
Dialogue: 0,1:28:32.13,1:28:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,把手拿开
Dialogue: 0,1:28:40.68,1:28:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,比我想像的胸部还好啊
Dialogue: 0,1:28:47.22,1:28:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,前辈别那么淫荡好吗
Dialogue: 0,1:28:51.89,1:28:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,这母亲真棒
Dialogue: 0,1:28:55.36,1:28:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,很棒吧
Dialogue: 0,1:28:56.43,1:28:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,乳头乳头
Dialogue: 0,1:29:00.30,1:29:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,拿着快点快点
Dialogue: 0,1:29:04.70,1:29:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,放开我
Dialogue: 0,1:29:14.31,1:29:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,漂亮
Dialogue: 0,1:29:15.78,1:29:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,真的很棒哦
Dialogue: 0,1:29:17.78,1:29:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,很漂亮哦
Dialogue: 0,1:29:19.92,1:29:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,1:29:22.85,1:29:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,很漂亮哦叫什么名字
Dialogue: 0,1:29:28.59,1:29:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,咲
Dialogue: 0,1:29:29.93,1:29:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,咲小姐漂亮哦
Dialogue: 0,1:29:37.67,1:29:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,敏感程度也很棒唉
Dialogue: 0,1:29:40.60,1:29:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,还有这边这边
Dialogue: 0,1:29:42.74,1:29:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,乳头就可以高潮哦
Dialogue: 0,1:29:44.21,1:29:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,1:29:47.14,1:29:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,好了帮你舔一下吧
Dialogue: 0,1:29:50.08,1:29:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,真的耶
Dialogue: 0,1:29:51.41,1:29:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,乳头都勃起了
Dialogue: 0,1:29:52.88,1:29:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,有点不妙吧
Dialogue: 0,1:30:02.09,1:30:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,好软
Dialogue: 0,1:30:18.51,1:30:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,好好让前辈见识一下吧
Dialogue: 0,1:30:27.45,1:30:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,来这一边
Dialogue: 0,1:30:32.79,1:30:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,超棒
Dialogue: 0,1:30:34.66,1:30:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,真的是太好了
Dialogue: 0,1:30:36.66,1:30:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,1:30:52.41,1:30:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,这屁股挺不错的
Dialogue: 0,1:30:59.21,1:31:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,像这种
Dialogue: 0,1:31:02.15,1:31:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以随意玩弄你的身体吧
Dialogue: 0,1:31:06.56,1:31:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,当然可以
Dialogue: 0,1:31:15.36,1:31:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,来这边来一点
Dialogue: 0,1:31:18.30,1:31:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,快停下来
Dialogue: 0,1:31:20.04,1:31:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,来让我们好好玩一下吧
Dialogue: 0,1:31:22.04,1:31:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,躺下来
Dialogue: 0,1:31:27.38,1:31:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,挺好的呀
Dialogue: 0,1:31:31.38,1:31:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,没想过你居然生过孩子
Dialogue: 0,1:31:33.52,1:31:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是这样子的
Dialogue: 0,1:31:36.72,1:31:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,可以拍照吗
Dialogue: 0,1:31:37.92,1:31:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,1:31:40.32,1:31:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,都已经湿透了 你看
Dialogue: 0,1:31:43.93,1:31:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,1:31:48.46,1:31:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,来这边来拍照
Dialogue: 0,1:31:50.73,1:31:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,这边来在这边来拍照
Dialogue: 0,1:31:53.27,1:31:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,不要这样子
Dialogue: 0,1:31:56.34,1:31:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,好好拍一张
Dialogue: 0,1:31:57.81,1:31:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,快把头抬起来
Dialogue: 0,1:31:59.27,1:32:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,快点来快点
Dialogue: 0,1:32:01.01,1:32:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,对对对
Dialogue: 0,1:32:04.08,1:32:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,还挺不错的哟
Dialogue: 0,1:32:05.55,1:32:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,等会再发给你
Dialogue: 0,1:32:08.48,1:32:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,超棒哎
Dialogue: 0,1:32:09.95,1:32:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,这边都已经湿透了
Dialogue: 0,1:32:12.49,1:32:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,不妙啊
Dialogue: 0,1:32:13.56,1:32:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,这屁股不得了
Dialogue: 0,1:32:15.96,1:32:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以摸吗
Dialogue: 0,1:32:17.43,1:32:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,请慢用
Dialogue: 0,1:32:19.16,1:32:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,来把屁股翘起来
Dialogue: 0,1:32:22.36,1:32:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,不要这样子
Dialogue: 0,1:32:23.57,1:32:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,1:32:31.71,1:32:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以呀
Dialogue: 0,1:32:33.84,1:32:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,阿姨你有没有舔过啊
Dialogue: 0,1:32:51.73,1:32:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,不行了不行了
Dialogue: 0,1:33:04.27,1:33:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不错不错
Dialogue: 0,1:33:16.82,1:33:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,高潮了吗
Dialogue: 0,1:33:18.82,1:33:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,高潮了吗
Dialogue: 0,1:33:20.56,1:33:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,高潮了吗
Dialogue: 0,1:33:21.36,1:33:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,好像高潮了
Dialogue: 0,1:33:22.16,1:33:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,阿姨呀
Dialogue: 0,1:33:24.29,1:33:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,来让我爽一下可以吗
Dialogue: 0,1:33:27.90,1:33:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,1:33:34.17,1:33:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,不要那么粗鲁嘛
Dialogue: 0,1:33:36.44,1:33:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,弄一下
Dialogue: 0,1:33:39.64,1:33:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,1:33:42.98,1:33:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,像平时那样子来
Dialogue: 0,1:33:43.78,1:33:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,没错没错
Dialogue: 0,1:33:46.98,1:33:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,自己来压住 继续爽快吧
Dialogue: 0,1:33:52.99,1:33:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,1:33:55.26,1:33:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒啊屁股都看了\N一清二楚了
Dialogue: 0,1:34:06.20,1:34:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,真受不了
Dialogue: 0,1:34:08.74,1:34:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服对吧
Dialogue: 0,1:34:11.27,1:34:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,很不妙啊
Dialogue: 0,1:34:18.08,1:34:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,手不要停下来
Dialogue: 0,1:34:29.29,1:34:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,前辈你应该很舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,1:34:32.09,1:34:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系的啦
Dialogue: 0,1:34:34.36,1:34:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,1:34:54.52,1:34:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,1:34:59.05,1:35:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,老妈
Dialogue: 0,1:35:03.33,1:35:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,老妈
Dialogue: 0,1:35:12.13,1:35:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,这我也想要
Dialogue: 0,1:35:15.34,1:35:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,屁股都己经掰开了\N你看看小穴这边
Dialogue: 0,1:35:22.54,1:35:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是很开心吗
Dialogue: 0,1:35:26.01,1:35:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,是不是很棒啊感觉
Dialogue: 0,1:35:28.68,1:35:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,那是不是很爽啊
Dialogue: 0,1:35:32.02,1:35:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧来吧来吧
Dialogue: 0,1:35:37.63,1:35:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你们在干什么快点下来
Dialogue: 0,1:35:40.96,1:35:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧走吧走吧
Dialogue: 0,1:35:47.10,1:35:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,正人
Dialogue: 0,1:35:54.18,1:35:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,村上
Dialogue: 0,1:35:55.51,1:35:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,这是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,1:35:58.71,1:36:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,他的儿子
Dialogue: 0,1:36:00.58,1:36:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,这也过分了吧
Dialogue: 0,1:36:02.58,1:36:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,等一等
Dialogue: 0,1:36:05.52,1:36:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,先把它搞定
Dialogue: 0,1:36:08.46,1:36:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,快停下了你们
Dialogue: 0,1:36:11.93,1:36:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,快点停下来
Dialogue: 0,1:36:14.06,1:36:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,正人
Dialogue: 0,1:36:18.87,1:36:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,快放了他
Dialogue: 0,1:36:22.07,1:36:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,快放了我吗
Dialogue: 0,1:36:25.67,1:36:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,别乱动啊
Dialogue: 0,1:36:28.08,1:36:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,不要紧吧你
Dialogue: 0,1:36:31.41,1:36:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,快点停下来你们这些人
Dialogue: 0,1:36:34.62,1:36:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我有一个很好的想法
Dialogue: 0,1:36:37.95,1:36:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你有什么想法
Dialogue: 0,1:36:39.55,1:36:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你稍微看一下吧
Dialogue: 0,1:36:46.63,1:36:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你们快停下来
Dialogue: 0,1:36:49.16,1:36:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,像这样子来
Dialogue: 0,1:36:51.30,1:36:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,1:36:54.10,1:36:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,快放开我吗
Dialogue: 0,1:36:56.77,1:36:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,给我闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,1:37:01.71,1:37:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,有感觉了
Dialogue: 0,1:37:03.58,1:37:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,阿姨把头抬起来
Dialogue: 0,1:37:07.05,1:37:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你应该感受得到吧\N被后面干了
Dialogue: 0,1:37:12.39,1:37:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,快停下来
Dialogue: 0,1:37:21.86,1:37:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,快点发过来吗
Dialogue: 0,1:37:25.33,1:37:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你看一看吧
Dialogue: 0,1:37:28.54,1:37:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,放开我妈
Dialogue: 0,1:37:32.81,1:37:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你老妈真舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:37:36.68,1:37:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你再吵就让你知错
Dialogue: 0,1:37:39.35,1:37:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,1:37:49.09,1:37:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,阿姨前辈的肉棒怎么样
Dialogue: 0,1:37:53.76,1:37:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,快停下来
Dialogue: 0,1:37:56.43,1:37:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,快点停下来啊
Dialogue: 0,1:37:58.03,1:38:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,快来吧快点
Dialogue: 0,1:38:01.24,1:38:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,这边还有呢来来来快点
Dialogue: 0,1:38:07.64,1:38:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,1:38:20.06,1:38:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,挺不错的吧
Dialogue: 0,1:38:22.06,1:38:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,快停下来
Dialogue: 0,1:38:24.19,1:38:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,这家伙感觉快死了
Dialogue: 0,1:38:31.53,1:38:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,1:38:32.87,1:38:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你好吵啊
Dialogue: 0,1:38:34.87,1:38:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,快停下来
Dialogue: 0,1:38:37.41,1:38:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,1:38:39.01,1:38:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,1:38:41.54,1:38:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,快停下来
Dialogue: 0,1:38:44.08,1:38:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,好烦啊 前辈这家伙
Dialogue: 0,1:38:46.62,1:38:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,1:38:47.42,1:38:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你们快停下来
Dialogue: 0,1:38:49.15,1:38:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,那怎么玩
Dialogue: 0,1:38:51.55,1:38:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧你懂的
Dialogue: 0,1:38:53.82,1:38:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,这主意挺不错的
Dialogue: 0,1:38:55.69,1:38:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,这是天才般的主意
Dialogue: 0,1:39:03.16,1:39:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧来吧
Dialogue: 0,1:39:05.70,1:39:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,挺好的不是吗
Dialogue: 0,1:39:07.57,1:39:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,1:39:10.64,1:39:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,1:39:16.65,1:39:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,表现真不错
Dialogue: 0,1:39:23.99,1:39:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,1:39:25.99,1:39:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,有点不妙啊你看
Dialogue: 0,1:39:34.40,1:39:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,挺好的这两位不是很像吗
Dialogue: 0,1:39:37.73,1:39:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,挺像的吧
Dialogue: 0,1:39:38.93,1:39:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,不愧是母子俩
Dialogue: 0,1:39:45.07,1:39:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,这样看的不是很清楚
Dialogue: 0,1:39:48.81,1:39:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,这是第1次见到这样的对吧
Dialogue: 0,1:39:52.81,1:39:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧好好来弄一下吧\N快点来
Dialogue: 0,1:39:57.49,1:39:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,好好的舔一舔
Dialogue: 0,1:40:02.56,1:40:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,他准备好了吗
Dialogue: 0,1:40:11.77,1:40:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,真的很开心对不对啊
Dialogue: 0,1:40:16.17,1:40:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,不要快停下来
Dialogue: 0,1:40:22.18,1:40:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊不要啊
Dialogue: 0,1:40:24.98,1:40:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你看这还很多哟
Dialogue: 0,1:40:26.18,1:40:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,准备好了吗
Dialogue: 0,1:40:31.65,1:40:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊快停下来啊
Dialogue: 0,1:40:36.99,1:40:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,好好弄一下快点来舔一舔
Dialogue: 0,1:40:40.60,1:40:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,可以吗
Dialogue: 0,1:40:41.40,1:40:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,那在他眼前来搞
Dialogue: 0,1:40:49.14,1:40:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,还挺不错的
Dialogue: 0,1:40:53.01,1:40:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧阿姨
Dialogue: 0,1:40:58.08,1:41:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你老妈的小穴好舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,1:41:17.70,1:41:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害你看看这边还有
Dialogue: 0,1:41:21.17,1:41:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,1:41:22.10,1:41:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,这屁股真棒
Dialogue: 0,1:41:34.78,1:41:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,超棒
Dialogue: 0,1:41:36.92,1:41:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,有点不妙
Dialogue: 0,1:41:46.26,1:41:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,再来一次吗
Dialogue: 0,1:41:52.40,1:41:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧来吧这边来快点来
Dialogue: 0,1:42:01.48,1:42:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,超开心的样子
Dialogue: 0,1:42:06.55,1:42:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,1:42:08.42,1:42:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,真是很棒
Dialogue: 0,1:42:11.62,1:42:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,1:42:14.82,1:42:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧硬梆梆的
Dialogue: 0,1:42:18.03,1:42:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,看起来很舒服的样子哦
Dialogue: 0,1:42:20.96,1:42:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,都夹住了
Dialogue: 0,1:42:22.03,1:42:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,可以吗
Dialogue: 0,1:42:26.43,1:42:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,来帮我夹住
Dialogue: 0,1:42:28.17,1:42:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,快点来吧
Dialogue: 0,1:42:33.78,1:42:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,1:42:35.51,1:42:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,真棒
Dialogue: 0,1:42:40.85,1:42:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,根本看不出来啊
Dialogue: 0,1:42:43.12,1:42:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你看看这里你看
Dialogue: 0,1:42:44.72,1:42:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,这怎么能行呢
Dialogue: 0,1:42:46.32,1:42:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,1:42:51.26,1:42:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,想要把眼镜还给你吗
Dialogue: 0,1:42:59.13,1:43:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,对对对
Dialogue: 0,1:43:03.67,1:43:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,1:43:10.88,1:43:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,挺不错的
Dialogue: 0,1:43:11.68,1:43:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你也是
Dialogue: 0,1:43:14.08,1:43:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,好好的试一下吧
Dialogue: 0,1:43:17.69,1:43:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,该怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,1:43:20.22,1:43:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,把手放这边
Dialogue: 0,1:43:21.96,1:43:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我来过来这边
Dialogue: 0,1:43:23.16,1:43:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧起来一下快点快点
Dialogue: 0,1:43:26.49,1:43:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,没错就是这样子
Dialogue: 0,1:43:29.56,1:43:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,1:43:31.03,1:43:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,准备好了吗
Dialogue: 0,1:43:33.84,1:43:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,插进去了
Dialogue: 0,1:43:36.24,1:43:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,有点不妙
Dialogue: 0,1:43:38.91,1:43:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托了别看了
Dialogue: 0,1:43:48.38,1:43:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,看着老妈的小穴怎么样
Dialogue: 0,1:43:53.86,1:43:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,真的很棒这感觉
Dialogue: 0,1:43:59.33,1:44:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,不要这样子快点下来啊
Dialogue: 0,1:44:03.06,1:44:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,1:44:05.20,1:44:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,1:44:09.07,1:44:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,挺不错的哟
Dialogue: 0,1:44:19.75,1:44:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,自己都叫出来了
Dialogue: 0,1:44:26.02,1:44:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,来把这个来让我们看一下
Dialogue: 0,1:44:29.89,1:44:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,把这个软绵绵的胸部\N给我们看一下吧
Dialogue: 0,1:44:33.36,1:44:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧来吧
Dialogue: 0,1:44:44.97,1:44:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,1:44:46.17,1:44:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,这简直欲罢不能啊
Dialogue: 0,1:44:54.18,1:44:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,1:45:04.19,1:45:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,让我们看一下
Dialogue: 0,1:45:17.14,1:45:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,这就很有意思了
Dialogue: 0,1:45:19.54,1:45:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,对不对呀
Dialogue: 0,1:45:21.28,1:45:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,问你
Dialogue: 0,1:45:32.89,1:45:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,准备好了吗
Dialogue: 0,1:45:44.50,1:45:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,不行了已经不行了
Dialogue: 0,1:45:55.84,1:45:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,那让我来
Dialogue: 0,1:45:58.25,1:46:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,换人吧
Dialogue: 0,1:46:03.32,1:46:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,来好好开心一下吧
Dialogue: 0,1:46:18.00,1:46:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么啦你
Dialogue: 0,1:46:22.40,1:46:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,来救救你妈妈呀
Dialogue: 0,1:46:26.54,1:46:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你不救你妈我就上了呀
Dialogue: 0,1:46:33.75,1:46:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,那你看一下你看一下
Dialogue: 0,1:46:51.10,1:46:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,又要高潮了
Dialogue: 0,1:47:00.17,1:47:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,来好好继续吧
Dialogue: 0,1:47:03.11,1:47:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,慢慢来插进去了
Dialogue: 0,1:47:08.18,1:47:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,1:47:12.85,1:47:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,这个不得了啊这声音
Dialogue: 0,1:47:14.86,1:47:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,1:47:16.86,1:47:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,1:47:21.53,1:47:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害啊你看看弄进去了
Dialogue: 0,1:47:24.60,1:47:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经硬梆梆的了
Dialogue: 0,1:47:26.33,1:47:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,这胸部真棒
Dialogue: 0,1:47:34.88,1:47:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,搞什么鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,1:47:36.48,1:47:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,让他闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,1:47:39.28,1:47:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,1:47:45.82,1:47:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,好好努力哦
Dialogue: 0,1:47:54.36,1:47:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我们来玩点更恩爱的吧
Dialogue: 0,1:48:00.77,1:48:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧来吧
Dialogue: 0,1:48:11.85,1:48:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,好好看着哟
Dialogue: 0,1:48:15.58,1:48:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,1:48:17.45,1:48:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,看得见吗
Dialogue: 0,1:48:19.05,1:48:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,这家伙真没出息啊
Dialogue: 0,1:48:23.99,1:48:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,对对对
Dialogue: 0,1:48:25.59,1:48:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你不拯救你妈妈吗
Dialogue: 0,1:48:35.20,1:48:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,1:48:38.27,1:48:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,真是碍事
Dialogue: 0,1:48:46.28,1:48:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧来吧
Dialogue: 0,1:48:48.02,1:48:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,让他看看屁股
Dialogue: 0,1:48:50.02,1:48:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,看得很清楚吧
Dialogue: 0,1:48:54.69,1:48:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,那是不得了啊
Dialogue: 0,1:48:59.63,1:49:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,1:49:04.57,1:49:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,前辈我可以\N让他帮我舔一下吗
Dialogue: 0,1:49:07.37,1:49:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,可以呀
Dialogue: 0,1:49:09.50,1:49:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,来一个
Dialogue: 0,1:49:56.22,1:49:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,不觉得刚刚好吗现在
Dialogue: 0,1:50:01.29,1:50:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,要不要搞啊
Dialogue: 0,1:50:02.76,1:50:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,可以吗
Dialogue: 0,1:50:06.23,1:50:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,那就好好玩一玩吧
Dialogue: 0,1:50:09.16,1:50:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,1:50:12.23,1:50:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,超我舔一下吧
Dialogue: 0,1:50:17.71,1:50:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,1:50:23.18,1:50:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,真的很舒服啊阿姨
Dialogue: 0,1:50:27.18,1:50:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你妈说是为了你哦
Dialogue: 0,1:50:30.79,1:50:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你呀
Dialogue: 0,1:50:32.65,1:50:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,为了不让你被欺负
Dialogue: 0,1:50:35.46,1:50:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,来把腰抬起来一点
Dialogue: 0,1:50:38.93,1:50:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,可是很努力的在服侍哦
Dialogue: 0,1:50:47.34,1:50:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,1:50:48.80,1:50:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你看你母亲不行\N你这个儿子也不行
Dialogue: 0,1:50:58.28,1:50:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,真的好棒啊
Dialogue: 0,1:51:00.55,1:51:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样啊
Dialogue: 0,1:51:07.76,1:51:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,那跟我接吻吧
Dialogue: 0,1:51:26.97,1:51:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,1:51:29.91,1:51:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,1:51:39.65,1:51:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,1:51:40.32,1:51:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你就再猛烈一点吧
Dialogue: 0,1:51:41.66,1:51:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,来到这边来
Dialogue: 0,1:51:57.67,1:51:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,挺棒的
Dialogue: 0,1:52:01.14,1:52:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,真的是好棒啊
Dialogue: 0,1:52:08.22,1:52:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧一起爽一下吧前辈
Dialogue: 0,1:52:11.15,1:52:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,来这边这边
Dialogue: 0,1:52:14.36,1:52:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,来这边来吧
Dialogue: 0,1:52:35.98,1:52:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你爽哦
Dialogue: 0,1:52:39.85,1:52:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,这感觉真是好爽
Dialogue: 0,1:52:49.72,1:52:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,1:52:50.52,1:52:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样不错吧
Dialogue: 0,1:52:51.33,1:52:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,1:52:52.79,1:52:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,1:53:00.67,1:53:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,真是太爽了吧
Dialogue: 0,1:53:10.68,1:53:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,要射了
Dialogue: 0,1:53:25.63,1:53:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,1:53:31.63,1:53:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧\N阿姨这里当着你儿子的面
Dialogue: 0,1:53:35.37,1:53:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,来搞吧
Dialogue: 0,1:53:39.37,1:53:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,挺好的呀
Dialogue: 0,1:53:41.78,1:53:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,这表情真不错
Dialogue: 0,1:53:46.18,1:53:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,1:53:49.38,1:53:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,1:53:52.32,1:53:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,说话了吗
Dialogue: 0,1:53:54.86,1:53:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,1:53:56.86,1:53:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,1:53:59.26,1:54:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉什么
Dialogue: 0,1:54:03.93,1:54:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,说话呀
Dialogue: 0,1:54:09.80,1:54:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服啊抱歉
Dialogue: 0,1:54:16.08,1:54:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,1:54:17.01,1:54:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,阿姨
Dialogue: 0,1:54:18.61,1:54:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样要射了
Dialogue: 0,1:54:28.36,1:54:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,要射了
Dialogue: 0,1:54:36.50,1:54:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,真是浪费啊
Dialogue: 0,1:54:40.90,1:54:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,比我还射的快
Dialogue: 0,1:54:45.17,1:54:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,射的瞬间说一声啊
Dialogue: 0,1:54:49.98,1:54:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,1:54:53.18,1:54:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,那等我再爽一下吧
Dialogue: 0,1:54:55.58,1:54:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样前辈
Dialogue: 0,1:54:57.59,1:54:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧来吧来吧
Dialogue: 0,1:55:14.54,1:55:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,1:55:24.14,1:55:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,1:55:25.88,1:55:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,已经湿透了
Dialogue: 0,1:55:32.15,1:55:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,1:55:34.15,1:55:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,1:55:36.56,1:55:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,这表情真不错
Dialogue: 0,1:55:52.04,1:55:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,那一起爽一下
Dialogue: 0,1:55:56.84,1:55:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你可别挡住前辈
Dialogue: 0,1:56:00.71,1:56:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,好好在旁边看吧
Dialogue: 0,1:56:14.06,1:56:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,这真的很有感觉啊
Dialogue: 0,1:56:17.40,1:56:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,有点不妙受不了啊
Dialogue: 0,1:56:25.41,1:56:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,这是太棒了吧
Dialogue: 0,1:56:57.17,1:56:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,都已经吃饭了
Dialogue: 0,1:57:23.33,1:57:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,前辈这边可以洗澡哦
Dialogue: 0,1:57:26.53,1:57:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,来到这边
Dialogue: 0,1:57:33.34,1:57:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,太太
Dialogue: 0,1:57:34.94,1:57:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,以后会有更多朋友过来的
Dialogue: 0,1:57:38.28,1:57:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,请多关照哦
Dialogue: 0,1:57:55.76,1:57:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了对吧
Dialogue: 0,1:58:00.30,1:58:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你看你老妈为你做爱
Dialogue: 0,1:58:04.97,1:58:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你才不会被欺负
Dialogue: 0,1:58:07.91,1:58:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,好好的感谢你妈哟
Dialogue: 0,1:58:34.74,1:58:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,（奥田咲）

